{"tid":858970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果呢個世界上剩返呢三個女人俾你揀你會揀邊個？","createTime":"2018-10-12T07:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T07:59:15.000Z","uid":216286,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1541d9eef4ffd12917fe4882ef3ea6aa65145700","tid":858970,"uid":216286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"1)自己老母<br />\n2)林鄭月娥<br />\n3)李私煙<br />\n<br />\n冇得揀一世單身，冇得揀一世打飛機，揀完之後一定要有性行為，咁你會揀邊個？<br />\n利申：識揀一定揀李私煙，其實咁樣對比之下佢都唔算好差，起碼個樣可愛過林鄭，不過其實如果唔係林鄭堅持搞東大嶼嘅話我都可能會揀佢，有留意琴日佢伸懶腰嗰張相都知佢大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/152545_9f31b48edacab3fcacfddf0a49c7f6c0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F152545_9f31b48edacab3fcacfddf0a49c7f6c0.png&h=efc932e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/12/152613_292e684a53afe7a57b3c69e976c23601.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F12%2F152613_292e684a53afe7a57b3c69e976c23601.png&h=27b3b925&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1012df1bdb541e7965a692f64b5aaeb557399a71","tid":858970,"uid":65187,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"我會死撚左佢"},{"pid":"9b5b584df89dc03512ae8e4629db27682736a600","tid":858970,"uid":126690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a049e27534caa269af38a4b4674ff04b74c989d6","tid":858970,"uid":206416,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:32:13.000Z","msg":"我會揀你老母"},{"pid":"60f9a58a3b2e8b94a4aa75e4da56035e0ccc4440","tid":858970,"uid":206392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"可唔可以3個都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class